n                <p class=\"author\">- Maria Garcia, College Student</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Ready to Shine?</h2>\n            <p>Let us help you achieve your academic goals. Contact us for a free consultation.</p>\n            <a href=\"mailto:info@brightsparktutoring.com\" class=\"cta-button\">Contact Us Now</a>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 BrightSpark Tutoring. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}